Jean Lodge https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Lodge 0 Jean Lodge (born 4 August 1927) is an English stage, film and television actress.She played Guinevere in The Black Knight and Lady Netherden in The Hellfire Club.Lodge had two children with Alfred Shaughnessy. They are actor Charles and producer/actor David. Charles is best known for his role as Maxwell Sheffield on The Nanny.
